com.interpss.core.algo

Interface SimpleFaultAlgorithm

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, NameTag, NetworkRef<BaseAcscNetwork<?,?>>, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SimpleFaultAlgorithmImpl

    public interface SimpleFaultAlgorithm
extends NetworkRef<BaseAcscNetwork<?,?>>
    A representation of the model object 'Simple Fault Algorithm'. SC algorithm implementation class. It contains a list of Bus/Branch fault objects. It can be used to calculate multiple faults.

    The following features are supported:

    • Multi Factor
    • Sc Bus Voltage
    • Fault List
    See Also:
    CoreAlgorithmPackage.getSimpleFaultAlgorithm()
